fulltitle: What is Randy Brecker doing throughout this current state of lockdown and social distancing?
title: What is Randy Brecker doing throughout this current state of lockdown and social distancing?
description:
I got on Zoom this morning with Randy and asked him exactly that among several other topics. The short answer is that he's practicing. But you may be surprised by WHAT he's practicing.

To be notified about the launch of the full interview series called Jazz Master Summit
